# 🛒 ShopEase – Full Stack Inspired E-Commerce Website

![HTML](https://img.shields.io/badge/HTML5-Structure-orange)
![CSS](https://img.shields.io/badge/CSS3-Styling-blue)
![JavaScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/JavaScript-Logic-yellow)
![Frontend](https://img.shields.io/badge/Frontend-UI-green)
![Backend Logic](https://img.shields.io/badge/Backend-Simulated-purple)
![Netlify](https://img.shields.io/badge/Hosted%20on-Netlify-brightgreen)

**ShopEase** is a modern **E-Commerce Web Application** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.

The project demonstrates a complete **shopping workflow** including product browsing, cart management, checkout process, payment simulation, and order tracking.

Although the project is deployed as a **frontend application**, it simulates several **backend operations** such as cart storage, order management, and user session handling using JavaScript and browser storage.

---

# 🌐 Live Demo

🔗 **Website:**
https://codealpha-shopease.netlify.app

---

# 📌 Core Features

✔ Product category pages
✔ Product detail view
✔ Add to cart system
✔ Cart update & item removal
✔ Checkout process
✔ Payment page simulation
✔ Login & Signup interface
✔ Order confirmation page
✔ View previous orders
✔ Responsive design (mobile & desktop)

---

# ⚙️ Backend Simulation (Application Logic)

This project includes **backend-like functionality implemented using JavaScript**, such as:

• Cart data management
• Order storage and retrieval
• User login & signup logic
• Checkout workflow handling
• Dynamic UI updates based on user actions

Browser **LocalStorage** is used to simulate database behavior.

Example flow:

User → Select Product → Add to Cart → Checkout → Payment → Order Saved → View Order

---

# 🛠️ Technologies Used

| Technology           | Purpose                        |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| **HTML5**            | Structure of web pages         |
| **CSS3**             | Styling and layout             |
| **JavaScript (ES6)** | Business logic & interactivity |
| **LocalStorage**     | Simulated backend database     |
| **Netlify**          | Website hosting                |
| **GitHub**           | Version control                |

