# 🔄 Application Flow

1️⃣ User browses products
2️⃣ Selects product category
3️⃣ Opens product details
4️⃣ Adds item to cart
5️⃣ Proceeds to checkout
6️⃣ Completes payment simulation
7️⃣ Order is saved
8️⃣ User can view previous orders

